    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, resulting in a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish and professional ceramic coating. The interior is indistinguishable from new, with pristine leather surfaces, untouched trim, and that signature new-car scent. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history exclusively through certified technicians. Every button, seal, and component functions perfectly, offering a driving experience that is as tight and responsive as the day it was manufactured. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a turn-key, investment-grade example.",
      "price": 48500.0,
