    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in concours-level condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior upholstery, remains in showroom state. Meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment, this specimen offers an uncompromising driving experience for the discerning collector. We invite you to inspect what is arguably the finest example currently available on the market.",
