    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I have taken such incredible care of this car, and it is honestly in flawless shape\u2014it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot. It drives like an absolute dream and has been my total pride and joy. I'm so sad to see it go, but I'm looking for someone who will love it as much as I do. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
