    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black over Black Nappa leather. This specimen is powered by the S54B32 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing, paired with a desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. Mechanically, this vehicle is superlative: the rod bearings have been replaced, the VANOS system has been overhauled with upgraded seals, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced to ensure chassis rigidity. The factory limited-slip differential operates silently with perfect lock-up. Every suspension bushing remains compliant yet firm, preserving the original handling dynamics. The exterior retains its factory depth and gloss, while the interior shows no typical bolster wear or delamination. This is a turn-key, mechanically sorted icon for the serious collector.",
